3%B0%E6%98%8E%E5%BC%8Frestful%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AFwebapiclient%E5%9C%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 16 Jul 2018 09:02:35 +0000</pubDate><guid>/posts/%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E5%BC%8Frestful%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AFwebapiclient%E5%9C%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>自从项目上采用敏捷开发的流程以后，我们的开发任务中出现了不少“联调”的任务，而所谓的“联调”任务，完全是拜前后端分离所赐。通常来讲，按照前后</description></item></channel></rss>